column2: select plateifu, ra_MaNGA as RA, dec_MaNGA as DEC, i1_f_ap1 as i1, i2_f_ap1 as i2, i3_f_ap1 as i3, i4_f_ap1 as i4, m1_f_ap as m1, SQRT (POWER (( (ra_s-ra_MaNGA) *cos ((dec_MaNGA) * (#/#) )) , #) + (POWER ((dec_s-dec_MaNGA) , #) )) *# as AngSep into temp_manga from mydb.Spitzer_MaNGA_mpl7 where ra_s between (ra_MaNGA-#) and (ra_MaNGA+#) and dec_s between (dec_MaNGA-#) and (dec_MaNGA+#)
